{
  "name": "PublishObjects",
  "summary": "<p>每个 <strong>PublishObject</strong> 对象都代表保存为网页的工作簿中的某一项，并且还可以根据该对象中属性和方法所指定的值进行刷新。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Workbook/Workbook .htm#Workbook.PublishObjects\">PublishObjects</a></strong> 属性可返回 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PublishObjects/PublishObjects .htm#PublishObjects.PublishObjects\">PublishObjects</a></strong> 集合。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作簿中创建新的 PublishObject 对象，并将活动工作簿中的所有静态 PublishObject 对象保存到网页。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObjs = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>\n    publishObjs.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\示例1\\\\example.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;$A$1:$A$10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example_test&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= publishObjs.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (publishObjs.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">xlHtmlType</span> == xlHtmlStatic) {\n            publishObjs.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>()\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 <strong>PublishObjects</strong>(<em>index</em>)（其中 <em>index</em> 是工作簿中指定项的索引号）可返回一个 <strong>PublishObject</strong> 对象。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置第一张工作簿中第一个项的保存位置。本示例假定已经创建PublishObject对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filename</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\example1.html&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>工作簿中所有 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PublishObject/PublishObject .htm#PublishObject.PublishObject\">PublishObject</a></strong> 对象的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作簿上添加一个 PublishObject 对象，并显示当前活动工作簿 PublishObject 对象的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Work.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:D10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Book1.xls_130489&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Add",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>创建一个对象，该对象代表保存在网页上的文档中的项目。当对 ET 中的文档进行了一些自动修订时，这些对象可帮助随后对网页进行的更新。返回 <strong>PublishObject</strong> 对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿中第一季度工作表上的区域 D5：D9 保存到名为 Stockreport.html 的网页。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Server\\\\Stockreport.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;First Quarter&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;$D$5:$D$9&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Book1_4170&quot;</span>)\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n    publishObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoRepublish</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作簿上添加一个 PublishObject 对象，并显示当前活动工作簿 PublishObject 对象的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E:\\\\Work.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:D10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Book1.xls_130489&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "SourceType",
          "type": "XlSourceType",
          "description": "<p>源的类型。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "Title",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>用于保存源对象的 URL（在 Intranet 或网站上）或路径（本地或网络）。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Sheet",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>保存为网页的工作表名称。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Source",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>用来标识数据项的唯一名称，这些数据项的 <em>SourceType</em> 参数为下列常量之一：<strong>xlSourceAutoFilter</strong>、<strong>xlSourceChart</strong>、<strong>xlSourcePivotTable</strong>、<strong>xlSourcePrintArea</strong>、<strong>xlSourceQuery</strong> 或 <strong>xlSourceRange</strong>。如果 <em>SourceType</em> 为 <strong>xlSourceRange</strong>，则 <strong>Source</strong> 指定的是一个区域，该区域可以是一个已定义的名称。如果 <em>SourceType</em> 为 <strong>xlSourceChart</strong>、<strong>xlSourcePivotTable</strong> 或 <strong>xlSourceQuery</strong>，则 <em>Source</em> 指定的是图表、数据透视表或查询表的名称。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "HtmlType",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>指定项目是保存为交互式的 WPS Office Web 组件还是保存为静态文本和图像。可以为以下 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlHtmlType 枚举.html\">XlHTMLType</a></strong> 常量之一：<strong>xlHtmlCalc</strong>、<strong>xlHtmlChart</strong>、<strong>xlHtmlList</strong> 或 <strong>xlHtmlStatic</strong>。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "DivID",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>在 HTML DIV 标记中使用的唯一标识符，它用于标识网页上的项。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Title",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>网页的标题。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>一个代表新项目的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PublishObject/PublishObject .htm#PublishObject.PublishObject\">PublishObject</a></strong> 对象。</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除第一张工作簿上所有PublishObject对象，并显示删除后PublishObject对象的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果第一张工作簿上PublishObject对象的数量大于1，则删除该工作簿上所有PublishObject对象，然后将第一张工作簿中工作表Sheet1保存到名为 example1.html 的网页。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPublishs = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (objPublishs.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> &gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) {\n        objPublishs.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n    objPublishs.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceSheet, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\example1.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>)\n    objPublishs.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Item",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>从集合中返回一个对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例先在活动工作簿上新建 PublishObject 对象并保存到网页，然后从该网页 &lt;DIV&gt; 标记中获取标识符，并在名为D:\\\\example1.html的网页（通过保存某个工作簿得到的）中查找该行。然后，此示例还创建该网页的一个副本（D:\\\\example1.html），并在该副本的 &lt;DIV&gt; 标记前插入一个注释行。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObjects = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>\n    publishObjects.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceSheet, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\example1.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>)\n    publishObjects.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> strTargetDivID = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(publishObjects.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DivID</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> f1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">FreeFile</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Open</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\example1.html&quot;</span>, f1, jsInput)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">while</span> (!<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">EOF</span>(f1)) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> str = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LineInput</span>(f1)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (str.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">includes</span>(strTargetDivID) &amp;&amp; str.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">includes</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&lt;div&quot;</span>)) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&lt;!--Saved item--&gt;&quot;</span>)\n        }\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(str)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Close</span>(f1)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作簿上新建 PublishObject 对象，并将第一张工作簿上所有 PublishObject 对象的 Source 属性值赋值给单元格，然后将所有 PublishObject 对象保存到网页。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceQuery, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\示例1\\\\example.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ExternalData_1&quot;</span>, xlHtmlChart, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example_test&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPublish = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i)\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Cells</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Source</span>\n        objPublish.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>对象的名称或索引号。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "PublishObject"
    },
    {
      "name": "Publish",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>将电子表格中已添加到 PublishObjects 集合的项目的副本保存到网页。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果第一张工作簿上PublishObject对象的数量大于1，则将活动工作簿中的所有 PublishObject 对象保存到网页。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objPublishs = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (objPublishs.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> &gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) {\n        objPublishs.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作簿中创建新的 PublishObject 对象，并将活动工作簿中的所有 PublishObject 对象保存到网页。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> publishObjs = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PublishObjects</span>\n    publishObjs.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSourceRange, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\示例1\\\\example.html&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;$A$1:$A$10&quot;</span>, xlHtmlStatic, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example_test&quot;</span>)\n    publishObjs.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Publish</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
}